OL,4,CFujitsu sacked boss at height of
OL,5,CHorizon scandal
OL,6,GFujitsu, the company that built the
OL,7,Gflawed Horizon IT system, sacked a top
OL,8,Gboss at the height of the scandal.
OL,10,FRod Vawdrey, 67, was dismissed as
OL,11,FFujitsu's global president in 2014 for
OL,12,Fpersonal conduct issues, former
OL,13,Fcolleagues say.
OL,15,FHe returned to his native Australia,
OL,16,Fwhere he is now being sued for his
OL,17,Finvolvement in a "train wreck" stock
OL,18,Fmarket float which made him millions.
OL,20,FMr Vawdrey told the BBC he wasn't
OL,21,Finvolved in the Horizon project.
